data.description: Lowest priced pool home in Shadow Hills reduced for quick sale Plus new flooring! A beautiful  home in exceptional Sun City Shadow Hills active senior community. Desirable Montoya model in Phase 2. Move-in ready 2 bedroom plus den. Light & bright interior with 9' ceilings, every window with custom shutters.  Chef's kitchen with Kitchenaid appliances. Beautiful new luxury vinyl plank flooring installed 12/18/23 replacing all carpet. Custom bookcases in dining area, wrap around stool height dining bar. Primary suite overlooks pool; dual sinks, walk-in closet, spacious shower. 2nd bedroom next to den or office. Saltwater pool installed in 2018 has triple waterfalls, a tanning shelf & charming mosaics on bottom. Low maintenance landscaped private rear yard with pavers & lighting. Outdoor covered patio with misters. Warm & friendly Sun City Shadow Hills is a 24-hour guard gated community close to shopping and transportation. 2 clubhouses, a full 18 hole golf course & an executive 18 hole course, indoor & outdoor pools, over 60 clubs, pickleball, tennis, bocce, billiards, a library, restaurants, banquet hall, and entertainment. Low cost association fee just $337 per month includes cable TV & internet. Isn't it Time to Live Your Active lifestyle dream.?
